# Changelog for minihomelib

## [Unreleased]

### Added

- Add user sessions using log-in mechanism (Flask-Login, passlib)
- Add user interface translations
- Add basic stats

### Fixed

### Changed

- Enhanced UI: search (filter) and sort by column, book covers, new book arrivals
- Switched to flask.flash for message passing
- Switch to SQLite3 for book database
- Switch to TOML for configuration

### Removed

## [0.1.0] 2022-11-09

### Added
- Initial release